21 provisions of this section, the number of staff
22 implementing the provisions of this section, and
23 average daily classroom time devoted to implementing
24 the provisions of this section,
Req. No. 3701 Page 15

1 b. by grade, the number and percentage of all students in
2 kindergarten through third grade who did not meet
3 grade-level targets based on a screening instrument
